nd they wish me the same. Im thinking, whew... finally i got out of that heap of shit. <br><br>This morning... A necro in tides of valor Asks me if he can Dupe the cloak of flame i had gotten in tides before the patch... I mean jeez... im a troll but im not that stupid. If you really wanted it that bad, Just have faranor ask for it i was thinking.<br><br>Later this morning... Poldar, Faranors twin brother Asks me to give the cof back. I told him to have faranor give me a tell. So he does. He says give the cof back... Although i felt as if i earned it considering i was there when they got their cloaks of piety, I agreed to give th cloak back. And i did. Even though i couldve easily kept it... but id rather not deal with the bullshit that comes with me keeping it... All the retarded rumors... all the hate tells and what not... Id rather just move on and have fun with OTHER people. <br><br>Im not sure what im meaning to do here... Ask a question such as &quot;was this right&quot; or whatever for some support from your folks since i feel so betrayed... OR to just give anyone whos thinking about joining Tides a Decent warning... Well anyhow, Best of luck ToV... Please dont send me anymore tells.../bye<br><br><br>Blizz <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ukodimoo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kodimoo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Been around a while</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/10/02 5:27:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=804.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Things you do after leaving a guild...</span><hr size=1> its impossible to leave a guild on good terms<br><br>there is always a few who hate you.. just the way it is. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><s