 respect.<br><br>This game is PRESENT based, however, Not future based, not past based.  So, loot should clearly be awarded on the &quot;and if he get that he'll lose future arguments about whether he deserves the next piece of loot to someone who didn't get something&quot;.<br><br>Edit: HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA sigh...public computers and ezboards don't mix.....<br>This was Maniacles...haven't seen raftik here in a bit...<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><font face ="Balloon XBd BT">_______________________<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4782">Raftik</a><br><a href="http://www.casus-belli.net">Casus Belli</a></font></font></font></font></font></font></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uraftik.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raftik</A> at: 1/10/02 6:49:27 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/utaunto.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Taunto</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/10/02 6:56:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=804.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Things you do after leaving a guild...</span><hr size=1> /comfort Blizz <br>It's ok fatty, we can still own seb together <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><B><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6001">Taunto</A></B><br> 56th Gnome Myrmidon.<br><B><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=53347">Ocinel</A></B><br>56th Lizard Master.<br> <A HREF="http://www.ayonae-ro.net">Ayonae-Ro.</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% val